Package com.senacor.portal.sc.backend.exception

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomExceptionHandler
    Main exception handler before defalt 500 error is sent
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ActionForbiddenException
    Exception caught by exception handler and returned as 403 - forbidden
    AutomationRuleNotFoundException
    Exception thrown when AutomationRule is not found
    CategoryNotFoundException
    Exception for handling case that Category of Scorecard was not found
    DocumentGenerationException
    Exception for handling case that Document generation failed
    EmployeeNotFoundException
    Exception for handling case that Employee was not found
    ExchangeOutlookException
    Exception for handling case that Exchange outlook connection failed
    FeedbackNotFoundException
    Default exception thrown when feedback is not found in the database
    FisEndpointNoDataException
    Exception for handling case that some condition during request processing wasn't met
    GeneralBatchJobException
    Exception for handling case that there was a serious problem during FIS sync
    PayrollReportNotFoundException
    Exception for handling case that Payroll report was not found
    PhotoNotFoundException
    Exception to be thrown when user photo is not found
    PreconditionNotFulfilledException
    Exception caught by exception handler and returned as 412 - PRECONDITION FAILED
    RoleNotFoundException
    Exception for handling case that role does not exist
    ScNotFoundException
    Exception for handling case that SC was not found
    WrongInputException
    Exception caught by exception handler and returned as 400 - BAD REQUEST
